osition layer to form a patterned lattice buffer layer, and growing a nitride layer on the patterned lattice buffer layer. During the growth of the nitride layer, the patterned lattice buffer layer is removed to form an air gap at a portion of the nitride layer from which the patterned lattice buffer layer is removed. A nitride-based light emitting device manufactured thereby is also disclosed.
